name: E-toll Application Indonesia (EAI)
description: This is a mobile app design of a toll road service in Indonesia. Toll roads are operated by Jasa Marga, an Indonesian government-owned company. As a disclaimer, I don't work for Jasa Marga, the logo and color palettes are used for authenticity purposes. The company itself has launched a mobile application with the same purpose as EAI but I find the design and experience not pretty.
